itle=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-name\"><code>&lt;font-face-name&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-src\"><code>&lt;font-face-src&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-uri\"><code>&lt;font-face-uri&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>G\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>H\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/hkern\"><code>&lt;hkern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>I\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>J-L\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/linearGradient\"><code>&lt;linearGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>M\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/metadata\"><code>&lt;metadata&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section>\n<p>SVG <strong><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></strong> 要素は、テキストからなるグラフィクス要素を定義します。<code>&lt;text&gt;</code> には、他の SVG グラフィクス要素と同じように、グラデーション、パターン、クリッピングパス、マスク、またはフィルターを適用することができます。</p>\n<p>SVG 内でテキストが <code>&lt;text&gt;</code> 要素内以外で組み込まれた場合、レンダリングされません。これはデフォルトで隠されるのとは違い、<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/display\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">ディスプレイプロパティ (en-US)</a> を変更してもテキストは表示されません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用可能な場所","title":"使用可能な場所","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">カテゴリー</th><td>グラフィック要素 、 テキストコンテンツ要素</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">許可されている内容</th><td>任意の順で文字データと任意の数の以下の要素。<br><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element#animation_elements\">アニメーション要素</a><br><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element#descriptive_elements\">説明的要素</a><br><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element#text_content_child_elements\">テキストコンテンツの子要素</a><br><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a></td></tr></tbody></table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"グローバル属性","title":"グローバル属性","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#conditional_processing_attributes\">条件処理属性</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#core_attributes\">コア属性</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#graphical_event_attributes\">グラフィカルイベント属性</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#presentation_attributes\">プレゼンテーション属性</a> »</li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/class\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">class (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">style (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/externalResourcesRequired\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">externalResourcesRequired</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/transform\">transform</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"専用属性","title":"専用属性","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/x\">x</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/y\">y</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/dx\">dx</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/dy\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">dy (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/text-anchor\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">text-anchor (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/rotate\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">rotate (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/textLength\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">textLength (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/lengthAdjust\">lengthAdjust</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_インターフェイス","title":"DOM インターフェイス","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この要素は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SVGTextElement\"><code>SVGTextElement</code></a> インターフェイスを実装します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本的なテキストの使用例","title":"基本的なテキストの使用例","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"svg\">SVG</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>500<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>40<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 500 40<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>text</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>35<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">font-family</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Verdana<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">font-size</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>35<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Hello, out there\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"結果\">結果</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"基本的なテキストの使用例\" id=\"frame_basic_text_usage\" width=\"500\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text/_sample_.basic_text_usage.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"回転テキスト","title":"回転テキスト","isH3":true,"content":"<p>SVG テキストは回転することができます。</p>\n<h4 id